reviews.review_text:
Improvement from 3 to 4 stars This updated version is a major upgrade to my ears at least. That being said I always liked this show for the reason that love the shows that are so popular in the trading circles.
 Imagine if back in the day you had a chance to grab this one during the tape deck years of running off bootleg shows of our FAVORITE band ever. If it were the case today I think this would get more praise because it the 1st Woman R smarter and the sound captures every instrument .  I give it 3. 8 stars but going to post it as 4 because I want others to check it out.
